          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "這位年輕拳擊手在擂台上證明了自己是個有天分的鬥士。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Many fighters train for years before their first professional match.",
          "highlight": [
            "fighters"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "許多格鬥選手在接受第一場職業比賽前已經訓練多年。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "She was described as a real fighter who never gave up despite the setbacks.",
          "highlight": [
            "fighter"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "她被形容為一位真正的鬥士，儘管遭遇挫折也從不放棄。"
          }
        }
